# 1. Learning Path Home Screen

*(Wireframe: top-level experience of The Path of Objectivity)*

```
---------------------------------------------------
|  The Path of Objectivity                        |
|  Seeing clearly → Accepting reality → Acting cleanly |
---------------------------------------------------

[ Stage 1: See What Is ]   (progress bar: 40%)
  • Notice thoughts
  • Thought ≠ Reality
  • Emotional literacy
  • Clear perception

[ Stage 2: Accept What Is ]  (progress bar: 10%)
  • Allow the moment
  • Sit with discomfort
  • Let go of the story
  • Energy returns

[ Stage 3: Act on What Is ]  (locked or low progress)
  • Discernment
  • Boundaries
  • Aligned action
  • Self leads

---------------------------------------------------
[ Askesis: “Where are you right now?” ] (button)
---------------------------------------------------
```

**Core intention:**
Instant clarity about where the teen is in the path + a simple call to action:
**Askesis meets you where you actually are.**

