# 5. Reflection + Tracking Screen (Daily Use)

*(Wireframe: integrates Game of Life + Objectivity Path)*

```
---------------------------------------------------
DAILY OBJECTIVITY CHECK-IN
---------------------------------------------------

1. What actually happened today?
[ short text box ]

2. What was your mind saying about it?
[ short text box ]

3. Did you accept the moment or resist it?
( ) accepted
( ) resisted
( ) mixed

4. What action did you take?
[ text box ]

---------------------------------------------------
Skill Bar (auto-updates):
[ SEE    ████████▌      ]
[ ACCEPT ███▌            ]
[ ACT    ██               ]
---------------------------------------------------

[ Askesis Suggestion ]
"Would you like to review a situation right now?"
---------------------------------------------------
```

**UX intention:**
Daily reflection connects the path to *life lived*.
The bars show progress invisibly, subconsciously shaping behavior.

